0Z","msg":"識玩"},{"pid":"beca378a2683a292ff17717ad561d7cbc284827f","tid":432791,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:39:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結論係 公投係第一步 武裝係下一步<br />\n冇後台撐真係難</blockquote><br />\n庫爾德有武裝都好艱難<br />\n事關敵人都太多"},{"pid":"cf5144014075a0a889d3c8b180d056d5a068c758","tid":432791,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:44:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛災難警報<br />\n勿回奶西妖post</span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"5324902a136a18a01a1cd0a38de5c51e42f56fc1","tid":432791,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>結論係 公投係第一步 武裝係下一步<br />\n冇後台撐真係難</blockquote><br />\n庫爾德有武裝都好艱難<br />\n事關敵人都太多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n情況唔同<br />\n始終係歐洲地方,會有好多左膠<br />\n仲要係歐豬四國之一<br />\n自己經濟已經唔多好,打內戰對西班牙嚟講一定係下下之策<br />\n所以武裝反而可以暫緩<br />\n<br />\n但係最怕就係歐盟同其他國家全部都制裁加泰隆尼亞<br />\n如果樣樣嘢都禁運就大件事<br />\n唔洗多,禁運石油天然氣呢啲已經夠死"},{"pid":"81fd81b729521b6dc38ead980abb61f60644db80","tid":432791,"uid":29625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:43:47.000Z","msg":"無後台都預咗笠水㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7cf9428b167faa575b43b067cde77eb6c621c7e","tid":432791,"uid":97814,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:49:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfb135d7de777c8dba421d24c0b32f61d533fea2","tid":432791,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大巴大巴車落講獨撚度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收皮啦你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家西班牙有話要打鳩加泰咩?"},{"pid":"cf92d84f415c4ec299883eb277838ba3e99bd784","tid":432791,"uid":47352,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T19:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><bl